				\begin{document}$$33\%$$\end{document} of the free carriers photogenerated form the interlayer excitons. The exciton dynamics are similar to excitation with 1.03 eV photons. However, because the free-carrier dynamics is slower with 3.1 eV excitation, more excitons are generated.
